{"tid":741704,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家拍左幾耐拖先會有進一步？","createTime":"2018-07-14T02:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T05:10:53.000Z","uid":12754,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"157984e2a11439a55d576c5453976102c5b5479a","tid":741704,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:12:35.000Z","msg":"我同女朋友拍拖未夠一個月<br />\n<br />\n我地出街會拖手<br />\n會錫嘴 (佢唔比伸脷)<br />\n會上對方屋企攬埋一舊傾計再錫但唔比留過夜<br />\n住hall 個陣佢夜晚點都要返自己房<br />\n<br />\n想問大家拍幾耐拖先會有d進一步動作<br />\n例如伸下脷摸下胸<br />\n( 但佢又比我摸佢大脾，又會成個人訓落黎對波&rsquo;責&rsquo;住我，<br />\n又會拉我隻手臂埋埋佢對波)"},{"pid":"a2971908ebae3c34c29fcb5e468a123b401ee9bc","tid":741704,"uid":179547,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:14:54.000Z","msg":"樓主順其自然啦，差唔多啦"},{"pid":"a9e9974c575639b331134acbd2e6d0af9c16c08b","tid":741704,"uid":131618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:18:17.000Z","msg":"拍多幾次拖就可以掌握節奏<br />\n多練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041fda8f637f5f36d68fbe1085cd9a18c6b29743","tid":741704,"uid":71166,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:20:27.000Z","msg":"屌 鹹濕仔扑嘢就扑嘢啦<br />\n進一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ef270475ed6ce2aefd40e62a7db864f19c1123","tid":741704,"uid":193314,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:21:32.000Z","msg":"唔好催女朋友啊 比佢順其自然甘啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n情到濃時自然都會進一步 <br />\n慢慢黎啦"},{"pid":"748a0d5bb944df27b0920b7c4fceda9317b66fe3","tid":741704,"uid":117947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"問下佢濕未<br />\n佢READY好, 咁你咪準備進入正題囉"},{"pid":"37c35047189e7b11da194c9aa873e292a71224f1","tid":741704,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quo